{"url": "ew.com/movies/2017/01/27/john-hurt-dead-celebrities-react/", "text": "Veteran British actor John Hurt, who starred in such memorable franchises as Alien and Harry Potter, died Wednesday at age 77.\n\nUpon the news of the Hurt\u2019s death, many celebrities paid tribute to the actor on social media. Mel Brooks, Kiefer Sutherland, Sharon Stone, and Elijah Wood were just a few of those to share their memories and thoughts about Hurt.\n\n\u201cJOHN HURT. Simply an inspiration to all of us artists,\u201d wrote Vincent D\u2019Onofrio, along with four images of Hurt. \u201cHopefully his skill in acting will influence many actors in the future for a long long time.\u201d\n\nSee more reactions below.", "images": ["https://ew.com/thmb/S2WMJmGAEVi6U9wV6tGT63_EBCU=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/106_j_09935-2000-1dac5084e68244089c700416cbba4c0f.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/1TGAEFoy_irdB6krHX5_TyXcoUc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Paul-Reubens-080423-764f3f40e991476fbf7ec1a9c641eb43.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/o85ObDab7TokgH2DUIvu5S8wsig=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/alien-2000-84837aadabac4529be5092dbe9b267c2.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/u-uu_jDhDRYNapwBwFnyzwXD-WE=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Horror-movies-on-Hulu-071323-2d02da77b4584e598f8ba50829e0fa87.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/cFSzxBFCnmd9g9FkMSzI7x_TNCM=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Stars-We-Lost-110223-2-48ba871745e8448bb3807133e2171dab.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/iVp89Sw3b0Qc6lXwVL2BHvERj_Q=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Sci-fi-movies-on-Hulu-split-080123-67dcb838fa334b3980b0079051374343.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/64k6P1n3ADSpYVDD27MI45LYWfc=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Evil-Dead-Rise-031423_2-147bbd5e4d5e470ba2757e6b6ad304bf.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/nhLt_yod5Y41OWbxzeM2mvPuQis=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max